Website
China Dongxiang (Group) Company Limited


China Dongxiang (Group) Company Limited (SEHK: 3818) is a public company listed on the main board of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong. It is engaged in the design and sales of sports apparel and accessories in China. It owns all the rights to Kappa products in Mainland China, Macau and Japan and owns the Phenix, Inhabitant brands in Japan. [1][2][3]
